                        <p class="A15ProductContentText">In Singapore our main business marine markets are  solutions for Yachts,  Cruise Liners Ships, Commercial Vessels Ships, offshore Rig Platforms, Tankers,  Cargo Ships whereas in other nearby countries such as Indonesia and Malaysia the range of marine soundproofing works is much more extensive because of the labour costs are cheaper so there is more work going through the ship yards.</p>
