                        <p class="A15ProductContentText">We can then in most cases give you an  estimate based on this information. In some cases you may prefer to have one of  our Consultants come out for a site visit. Site visits to any offshore vessel  or entity of the port   of Singapore will fall  under our offshore site visit policy.</p>
